data.description: This MOVE IN READY 4/Bed 2.5/Bath + Loft is better than new!  Located in popular and booming Whitestown this home will be sure to please! Your new home offers builder upgrades no longer available and make sure to ask your agent for the FULL page of improvements made above and beyond those upgrades. Talk about checking all the boxes! As you enter you will feel the warmth and comfort of this layout. From the spacious great room to the beautiful kitchen and cozy home office this first floor is functional.  Upstairs you will find an open loft and four bedrooms with great size and layout. Looking for a large master with an amazing closet YOU GOT IT! Outside you'll enjoy your private fenced in backyard, metal gazebo with outdoor fan, 320 sq ft pa
